  "remarks": "JSC NMZ (a.k.a. Nizhny Novgorod Machine-Building Plant) is a Russian military-industrial state enterprise that develops artillery systems and missile systems, including the S-300 anti-aircraft missile systems, deployed by the Russian Armed Forces. Moreover, JSC NMZ is part of the Almaz-Antey concern, a Russian state-owned arms manufacturer that develops anti-aircraft defence and cruise missile systems for the Russian military.",
